The paper discusses the design and implementation of a storage and compute cloud for processing large-scale distributed data, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). The paper also mentions the use of MapReduce-style programming, which is commonly used in Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) and Database Systems (cs.DB). Additionally, the paper discusses experimental studies comparing Sector/Sphere to Hadoop, which could fall under Computer Engineering (cs.CE) or Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI).
